

<section xml:id="ch06_03_psurfaces">
  <title>Parametric Surfaces</title> <!-- : <me f\colon {\mathbb{R}}^2\to {\mathbb{R}}^3 </me></title> -->
  <introduction>
    <p>
      We now increase the number of inputs from 1 to 2. This will allow us to graph many space curves at the same time.
    </p>
  </introduction>
  
  <subsection>
    <title>Exploration Exercises</title>

    <todo>\larsonfive{More practice in Larson 15.5:16.}
